snippet.title: Labyrinth- Update Trailer
snippet.description:
Make your way through the procedural mazes of the Labyrinth. Compete with friends on the leaderboards as you rack up points and battle for the title of the Lord Of The Maze.

Music
Better Days - www.bensound.com
Bustin Loose - www.audionautix.com

Get Labyrinth on the Google Play Store: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.sabbathworks.labyrinth
